  <brief_title>Nasal Provocation Test With Lysine-Acetylsalicylate (ASA) in Patients With Nonsteroidal Anti-Inflammatory Drugs (NSAIDs) Hypersensitivity</brief_title>
  <official_title>Association Between Nasal Provocation Test With Lysine-Acetylsalicylate(ASA) and Clinical Diagnosis in Patients With Aspirin/Nonsteroidal Anti-Inflammatory Drugs(NSAIDs) and/or Acetaminophen Immediate Sensitivity Reactions</official_title>
