  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to compare the efficacy of nasal provocation test with
      Lysine-Acetylsalicylate in patients with history of NSAIDs hypersensitivity between
      mucocutaneous symptoms and respiratory symptoms and laboratory outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
